<p>I'm going to pass in 1 billion, written using the shorthand <code>1e9</c=
ode>, so it takes a
noticeable amount of time to run. Press the <h- key=3D"run"></h-> button be=
low to
measure how long it takes to calculate the sum of 1 to 1 billion.</p>
<s-code-timer label=3D"sum(1e9)" role=3D"figure" aria-label=3D"Timing how l=
