<h2 id=3D"putting-this-knowledge-to-work"><a class=3D"anchor" href=3D"https=
://samwho.dev/big-o#putting-this-knowledge-to-work">#</a>
Putting this knowledge to work</h2>
<p>In the previous sections of this post I've described the difference betw=
